1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:58,800
I didn't expect you to come.

3
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,360
I didn't either.

4
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:10,880
You came to ask who you really are,

5
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:12,440
right?

6
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:16,000
No.

7
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:18,720
I came to find you

8
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:20,760
to ask

9
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:24,960
where Wu Wangyan is.

10
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,600
Even this Moon Summoning Pearl
can't find her.

11
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,920
Look at this Shilin Sect.

12
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,400
Over a thousand years,

13
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:40,560
there are too many power seals here.

14
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,480
Even I can't undo them.

15
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,200
And the Formless Moon

16
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:47,480
has existed since Nuwa's time.

17
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:55,080
There are also
too many ancient seals there.

18
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:59,400
A tiny Moon Summoning Pearl
could hardly do anything.

19
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,760
Greetings, Master Chi Wen.

20
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:23,920
What's wrong?

21
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:26,000
To our surprise, inside the Shilin Sect,

22
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,200
there is a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit.

23
00:03:29,640 --> 00:03:32,920
And it's hidden on one of us.

24
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,200
So it's you!

25
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:33,240
You must know
what I want to discuss with you.

26
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,080
Yes.

27
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,320
This secret

28
00:04:38,760 --> 00:04:41,120
has long been kept in my heart.

29
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:47,440
You were afraid
the other members would find out,

30
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,000
so you asked to see me alone.

31
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,400
Stop pretending, Jiu Ying.

32
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:56,840
Stop defiling her merciful face.

33
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:10,600
You are braver than I thought.

34
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:14,600
If I really carry
a fragment of Jiu Ying's spirit,

35
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:17,000
then doesn't that mean…

36
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,840
Jiu Ying knows everything about me?

37
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:39,720
Bai Ze's Eastern Purple Lightning
can suppress evil spirits.

38
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:41,480
Wear it,

39
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:44,640
and it can temporarily
suppress Jiu Ying's spirit.

40
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:17,160
Thank you.

41
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,320
Don't mention it.

42
00:06:25,520 --> 00:06:27,640
Aside from the two fragments
inside the Oracle Stone,

43
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:31,880
we've gathered all 78 fragments
in this world.

44
00:06:32,840 --> 00:06:36,640
I didn't expect the one
that remained lost all this time

45
00:06:37,240 --> 00:06:38,360
would be on you.

46
00:06:38,440 --> 00:06:40,360
I'm going to the Formless Moon
to save someone.

47
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:42,320
Maybe we can go together.

48
00:06:42,400 --> 00:06:45,400
We can destroy the last two fragments
in the Oracle Stone.

49
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:49,080
The Oracle Stone is a sacred stone
created by Pan Gu and Nuwa together.

50
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:51,840
Ordinary power can hardly damage it.

51
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,840
Only by gathering the Dragon Deity's Power

52
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:57,080
might there be a chance to destroy it.

53
00:06:59,000 --> 00:07:00,520
What about Wu Wangyan?

54
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:02,120
I promise you.

55
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,560
She will be saved.

56
00:07:05,760 --> 00:07:06,600
And

57
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,160
Lu Wuyi is there too.

58
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:12,280
We're about to enter the Sacred Spring.

59
00:07:12,800 --> 00:07:15,080
Why did the Queen summon Wangyan alone?

60
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:18,320
Hui,

61
00:07:19,000 --> 00:07:21,240
you're the closest to Wangyan.

62
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,720
Do you know what's going on?

63
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,600
I don't know.

64
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,000
Wangyan…

65
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:30,280
didn't tell me anything.

66
00:07:52,760 --> 00:07:54,360
It may be out of your reach

67
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:57,760
to deal with me.

68
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,280
I've been wondering

69
00:08:03,040 --> 00:08:05,880
why your memories were always fragmented

70
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,240
every time we entered the Sacred Spring.

71
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:12,720
Turns out you suspected me all along

72
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:16,680
and removed some memories
you didn't want me

73
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:19,120
and your sisters to know.

74
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,600
Right?

75
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:22,560
Yes.

76
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:29,120
But tonight, if I share
my memories with them,

77
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:31,040
all of them will know

78
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:34,159
that you are Jiu Ying.

79
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:38,080
You won't get the chance.

80
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:51,960
The Tenth Dragon Son

81
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:55,720
can help you kill Chi Wen.

82
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,880
You know too much.

83
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,520
You deserve to die.

84
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,640
Keep me alive…

85
00:09:11,920 --> 00:09:13,720
and I can help you.

86
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:16,040
I am his weakness.

87
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:19,880
He'll obey you for my sake…

88
00:09:19,960 --> 00:09:21,680
I need your help?

89
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:24,480
Have you forgotten

90
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:28,040
what I'm best at?

91
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,720
When I wiped out the Flood Dragon clan,

92
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:47,120
I transferred the spirit fragment in you

93
00:09:48,560 --> 00:09:50,800
into Wu Shiguang's body.

94
00:09:53,760 --> 00:09:54,800
No way…

95
00:09:55,800 --> 00:09:58,760
Then how did you appear
in the Oracle Stone?

96
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:03,440
The Oracle Stone has three fragments.

97
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,200
Back then,

98
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:10,200
one fragment was used to control you
to slaughter the Flood Dragon clan.

99
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,000
The rest remain

100
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:14,360
in the Oracle Stone.

101
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,160
You're right, though.

102
00:10:23,760 --> 00:10:27,720
Keeping you alive
can indeed be his weakness.

103
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,120
No.

104
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,200
Get close to Wu Shiguang.

105
00:10:56,960 --> 00:11:01,240
Try to get his prayer beads
and bring them to me.

106
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,080
So you and the Dragon Deity

107
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,640
have been plotting all along.

108
00:11:37,280 --> 00:11:40,600
I will find out the truth
and prove Wangyan hasn't betrayed us.

109
00:11:40,680 --> 00:11:41,680
Wangyan,

110
00:11:41,760 --> 00:11:45,080
why are you so fragrant today?

111
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:48,480
You deceived Wangyan,
using her to do your work.

112
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:50,280
What's your purpose exactly?

113
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:53,680
When we go back
and enter the Sacred Spring,

114
00:11:53,760 --> 00:11:55,520
your plan with Wangyan

115
00:11:55,600 --> 00:11:57,040
will be known by the Queen.

116
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,360
Without memory sharing,

117
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,840
would you tell your Queen?

118
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,440
Wangyan.

119
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:53,600
Everything I said
to the Dragon Deity was a lie.

120
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,840
I was just playing along

121
00:12:58,320 --> 00:13:01,040
to carry out the Queen's mission.

122
00:13:01,120 --> 00:13:02,080
Really?

123
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:19,360
Greetings, Master.

124
00:13:35,680 --> 00:13:38,040
I'm sorry, Master.

125
00:13:41,560 --> 00:13:43,600
I ask to quit the Dragon-Slaying mission.

126
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:46,880
See?

127
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:52,560
The fated one can't escape fate after all.

128
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,320
Master,

129
00:13:58,160 --> 00:13:59,560
what exactly does

130
00:14:02,240 --> 00:14:03,720
"fated one" mean?

131
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:08,520
When the time comes, you'll understand.

132
00:14:11,640 --> 00:14:12,720
Where's Wangyan?

133
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:15,240
Where did she go?

134
00:14:18,760 --> 00:14:20,120
She's…

135
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:23,040
in quiet reflection.

136
00:14:33,440 --> 00:14:34,720
There's no moon tonight.

137
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:41,200
The moon is always there,
just hiding for now.

138
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:46,120
The other moons are all bright and clear.

139
00:14:46,760 --> 00:14:49,520
Poets write verses praising them.

140
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,720
Do you think

141
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,760
that moon no one can see

142
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,280
would feel sad?

143
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:01,800
What other moons?

144
00:15:03,600 --> 00:15:07,360
There is only one moon,
just in different phases.

145
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,600
We…

146
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,960
are one.

147
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:20,880
Wangyan,

148
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:23,760
if one day,

149
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:26,560
no one can see me anymore,

150
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:29,400
will you remember me?

151
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:31,480
Silly,

152
00:15:33,440 --> 00:15:35,040
we'll be together forever.

153
00:16:30,640 --> 00:16:31,640
Wuyi,

154
00:16:32,640 --> 00:16:33,720
I'm sorry…

155
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:41,240
I lied to you.

156
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:43,320
No need to apologize.

157
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,080
I lied to you too.

158
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,640
The Queen had me watch you.

159
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:55,600
I know about your partnership

160
00:16:56,920 --> 00:16:57,920
with Ji Ling.

161
00:17:04,319 --> 00:17:06,040
So you told the Queen?

162
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:14,000
Do you hate me?

163
00:17:14,599 --> 00:17:15,440
No.

164
00:17:18,359 --> 00:17:19,839
I could never hate you.

165
00:17:24,359 --> 00:17:26,400
Aren't you going to ask why I'm here?

166
00:17:27,359 --> 00:17:28,880
If the Queen sent me to kill you,

167
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:30,920
you wouldn't hate me?

168
00:17:36,360 --> 00:17:37,440
No.

169
00:17:38,800 --> 00:17:40,720
If I die by your hand,

170
00:17:41,840 --> 00:17:43,080
at least it wouldn't hurt.

171
00:18:01,760 --> 00:18:02,880
Wu Wangyan…

172
00:18:05,280 --> 00:18:06,960
What do you really want?

173
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:11,560
I don't know.

174
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:14,920
But I know

175
00:18:16,200 --> 00:18:17,360
what I don't want.

176
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:19,640
Not even your life?

177
00:18:20,720 --> 00:18:22,160
Not even your own life?

178
00:18:34,480 --> 00:18:37,320
I don't want my hands
to be forever stained with blood.

179
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:41,040
I don't want Jiu Ying
to keep controlling me,

180
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:44,320
stirring up killing and hatred
in this world.

181
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:47,880
I don't want to be a moon…

182
00:18:51,800 --> 00:18:53,880
that only lights up mass graves.

183
00:19:15,360 --> 00:19:16,320
Do it.

184
00:19:37,840 --> 00:19:39,720
Wuyi, what's wrong?

185
00:19:43,800 --> 00:19:44,880
Wangyan…

186
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:49,360
I never told the Queen.

187
00:19:50,520 --> 00:19:52,360
I would never betray you.

188
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:55,040
I came to ask you…

189
00:19:57,120 --> 00:19:58,560
if you still remember…

190
00:20:01,800 --> 00:20:03,960
the words you once said to me.

191
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,280
I have never forgotten.

192
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:12,800
Then why did you leave me behind
and go alone?

193
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,320
Because this path…

194
00:20:21,000 --> 00:20:22,200
is too dangerous.

195
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:26,480
I didn't want you to walk it.

196
00:20:28,080 --> 00:20:31,800
Because my enemy is too terrifying.

197
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:33,960
So I couldn't tell you.

198
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,640
The danger…

199
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:43,440
the truth…

200
00:20:44,920 --> 00:20:46,200
even my guilt toward you…

201
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:49,760
None of it could be said.

202
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:53,520
Enemy?

203
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:56,920
Danger?

204
00:20:58,160 --> 00:20:59,600
You mean…

205
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:02,000
the Queen?

206
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:05,640
The Queen…

207
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:08,160
is Jiu Ying.

208
00:21:11,080 --> 00:21:12,480
When the real Queen passed,

209
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:15,680
her power had faded.

210
00:21:16,720 --> 00:21:19,120
We missed her so much,

211
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:24,200
so when Jiu Ying wore her skin
and showed up,

212
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:30,320
we deceived ourselves
into believing she had gained

213
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:33,840
the power of endless rebirth like us.

214
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:55,960
He impersonated the Queen,

215
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:58,840
faking the Oracle Stone's prophecy,

216
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:02,000
ordering us to sow killing
and hatred in this world.

217
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:05,000
He called it the balance of the world,

218
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:07,320
and we believed it without question.

219
00:22:08,000 --> 00:22:09,800
But Xiaowei saw through him.

220
00:22:13,440 --> 00:22:14,360
Wangyan,

221
00:22:15,440 --> 00:22:18,080
she is no longer the kind Queen we knew.

222
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:23,200
The Formless Moon is now filled
with only cruelty and slaughter.

223
00:22:25,120 --> 00:22:26,480
Let me go.

224
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:30,360
You should find a way and escape too.

225
00:22:33,360 --> 00:22:34,280
Xiaowei is a traitor.

226
00:22:35,040 --> 00:22:38,320
Can her words be trusted?

227
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:40,280
I am a traitor too.

228
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:45,000
Then do you believe my words?

229
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,640
Who dares trespass?

230
00:23:03,160 --> 00:23:04,880
Aren't you afraid of perishing?

231
00:23:06,560 --> 00:23:07,520
Dragon Deity?

232
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:11,320
Since you know who I am,

233
00:23:12,320 --> 00:23:13,760
why don't you back off?

234
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:16,600
The Formless Moon is beyond this world,

235
00:23:17,320 --> 00:23:19,160
not bound by its rules.

236
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:22,480
We respect what you've done
for all living things,

237
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:25,160
but that doesn't mean we obey you.

238
00:23:25,840 --> 00:23:28,400
Master Dragon Deity, please leave.

239
00:23:29,680 --> 00:23:30,800
Where is Wu Wangyan?

240
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:32,960
- Let her out.
- How dare you!

241
00:23:33,040 --> 00:23:36,400
Moon spirit invoked,
your radiance eternal, arise!

242
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:13,760
By the fox's call, lend me your souls!

243
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:22,200
Formless Moon members, come forth.

244
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:38,320
Kneel before me.

245
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:43,920
Obey me.

246
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,000
You guys go save them.

247
00:24:54,440 --> 00:24:55,320
I'll handle things here.

248
00:24:59,200 --> 00:25:00,160
Wu Wangyan?

249
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:01,840
Wu Wangyan!

250
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:16,240
I told you I would find you.

251
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:23,760
How did you know
where the Formless Moon is?

252
00:25:24,360 --> 00:25:25,280
Chi Wen knows.

253
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:35,440
He's here too?

254
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:37,880
Yes.

255
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:45,000
I want to know

256
00:25:46,360 --> 00:25:47,400
who I really am.

257
00:25:50,560 --> 00:25:51,720
Knowing who you can be

258
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:55,600
is more important than that.

259
00:25:57,320 --> 00:26:00,680
All memories are paths you've walked,

260
00:26:01,320 --> 00:26:05,080
a burden not worth turning back
to walk again.

261
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:08,680
Forward is the way to go.

262
00:26:09,640 --> 00:26:11,400
But if I don't know who I am,

263
00:26:13,600 --> 00:26:15,440
I don't know which way to go.

264
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:19,760
If you really want to know it,
just go ask that butterfly demon.

265
00:26:21,320 --> 00:26:22,600
I'm teaching him reason,

266
00:26:23,120 --> 00:26:24,240
but you're teaching him
to break the rules!

267
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,520
Master Chi Wen strictly forbids

268
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:29,080
anyone to approach the butterfly demon.

269
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,840
Why be so obedient?

270
00:26:31,920 --> 00:26:34,200
Li Jie, while Master is away,

271
00:26:34,280 --> 00:26:36,480
sneak in and find out.

272
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:37,920
What do you say?

273
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:20,280
Do you really think
you can easily take Wu Wangyan away?

274
00:27:22,280 --> 00:27:26,000
Do you really think
I'm here to save Wu Wangyan?

275
00:27:34,560 --> 00:27:36,280
Dragon hearts as one,

276
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,640
all to source return,

277
00:27:40,400 --> 00:27:42,920
all barriers break!

278
00:27:56,400 --> 00:27:57,880
It worked!

279
00:28:31,400 --> 00:28:35,640
Even the Dragon Deity's Power
can't break Jiu Ying's seal.

280
00:28:38,160 --> 00:28:40,640
Jiu Ying has been absorbing
the Oracle Stone's power,

281
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:41,680
growing stronger.

282
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:45,800
And Wu Shiguang only has two pieces
of the Dragon Deity's Power.

283
00:28:46,320 --> 00:28:47,360
It's not enough.

284
00:28:50,880 --> 00:28:52,120
I also have one piece inside me.

285
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:55,160
No!

286
00:28:55,240 --> 00:28:57,480
If you give it up, you'll die.

287
00:28:58,200 --> 00:28:59,880
Xiaowei and Wu Zhiqi died

288
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:02,760
because Yuan Wuhuo
forcibly took their Dragon Deity's Power

289
00:29:03,280 --> 00:29:04,640
and damaged their spiritual veins.

290
00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:08,280
If I give mine willingly, I'll be fine.

291
00:29:09,160 --> 00:29:12,560
Master Chi Wen saved me with this power

292
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:15,000
that was never mine.

293
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:19,320
Returning it is only right.

294
00:29:21,720 --> 00:29:22,920
Dragon hearts as one,

295
00:29:23,440 --> 00:29:24,680
all to source return,

296
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:26,960
all barriers break!

297
00:30:11,000 --> 00:30:12,440
From now on,

298
00:30:12,520 --> 00:30:15,160
you are neither demon nor human.

299
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:18,920
In this world,
you will be a unique existence

300
00:30:19,440 --> 00:30:21,320
and also the loneliest of its kind.

301
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,720
From this moment,

302
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:29,080
you are Chi Wen,
the last Dragon Deity in this world.

303
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:33,680
So how long must I deceive the world?

304
00:30:35,320 --> 00:30:38,440
Until the Dragon's tenth son
awakens as a true dragon,

305
00:30:38,960 --> 00:30:41,560
your duty will be done.

306
00:30:44,160 --> 00:30:47,640
I didn't come here to be your enemy,

307
00:30:48,560 --> 00:30:49,880
but to seek cooperation.

308
00:30:53,320 --> 00:30:54,640
Don't trust me?

309
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:58,280
If I hadn't told you
about Wu Wangyan's betrayal

310
00:30:58,880 --> 00:31:00,640
and the Taotie artifact,

311
00:31:01,160 --> 00:31:04,880
you might still be dancing
in her palm even now.

312
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,480
Since she has betrayed you,

313
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:11,280
all her memories are stored
inside the Taotie artifact.

314
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:12,960
If you don't believe me,

315
00:31:14,760 --> 00:31:16,160
you can see for yourself.

316
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:22,960
Wu Wangyan is pitiful.

317
00:31:23,760 --> 00:31:25,800
She trusted you, helped you,

318
00:31:26,480 --> 00:31:29,800
but never knew
she was just a pawn in your game.

319
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:33,760
For great goals, small costs are nothing.

320
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,440
But you're pitiful too.

321
00:31:38,440 --> 00:31:40,800
You're just a pawn in Chi Wen's game.

322
00:31:41,880 --> 00:31:42,760
That's right.

323
00:31:45,080 --> 00:31:47,600
Chi Wen wants me
to wait for the tenth son,

324
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:52,280
then hand over the Dragon Deity's throne
I worked so hard to build.

325
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:56,640
All those centuries of suffering

326
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,320
would be a joke then?

327
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:02,520
So…

328
00:32:04,840 --> 00:32:08,160
Jiu Ying, we should work together.

329
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:11,680
My goal aligns with yours,

330
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,320
to slay the dragon deity.

331
00:32:16,560 --> 00:32:20,840
Even if Chi Wen dies,
there's still the tenth son.

332
00:32:22,120 --> 00:32:25,400
How could a false deity like you
ever take the throne?

333
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:31,200
I intended to seize
the Dragon Deity's Power

334
00:32:31,280 --> 00:32:32,600
to stop Wu Shiguang from rising.

335
00:32:33,560 --> 00:32:35,440
But Yuan Wuhuo meddled,

336
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:39,800
and things went awry,
unexpectedly helping Wu Shiguang.

337
00:32:41,040 --> 00:32:43,320
Since he's destined to be a dragon,

338
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:45,080
let him do the slaying.

339
00:32:46,240 --> 00:32:47,200
Besides,

340
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:51,000
doesn't this play right
into the self-protection

341
00:32:51,080 --> 00:32:53,640
they set up out of fear?

342
00:32:55,760 --> 00:32:57,400
Only the Dragon Deity's Power

343
00:32:58,040 --> 00:32:59,640
can kill a dragon deity.

344
00:33:01,680 --> 00:33:05,840
And that is such a grave crime

345
00:33:08,000 --> 00:33:11,560
that the slayer, too,
will be consumed by its curse.

346
00:33:13,360 --> 00:33:14,680
Then the throne

347
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:18,480
will be mine forever.

348
00:33:25,280 --> 00:33:26,800
What are you waiting for?

349
00:33:26,880 --> 00:33:29,480
You've been trapped
in Chi Wen's broken body

350
00:33:30,040 --> 00:33:30,880
for so many years.

351
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:34,600
You should know I didn't lie.

352
00:33:35,360 --> 00:33:36,200
Isn't that right?

353
00:33:37,320 --> 00:33:39,080
The Dragon's tenth son…

354
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:44,800
Only the Dragon Deity's Power
can slay a dragon deity.

355
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:48,480
So Jiu Ying will use the tenth son
to kill me,

356
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:53,280
so his true form
can break free from my body.

357
00:33:56,720 --> 00:33:58,040
The Dragon's tenth son?

358
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:00,880
Interesting.

359
00:34:04,880 --> 00:34:09,159
You also sent butterfly demons to seize
the tenth son from the Dragon Abyss.

360
00:34:14,159 --> 00:34:15,120
That's right.

361
00:34:28,719 --> 00:34:32,320
That outer-world being, Xie Lingxi,
is indeed something.

362
00:34:33,120 --> 00:34:35,960
However, he's too confident.

363
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:38,800
He thought hiding the son
among the flood dragons

364
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:42,440
with scales and horns too
would be safe enough

365
00:34:42,520 --> 00:34:43,840
to protect him.

366
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,120
Too bad.

367
00:34:46,880 --> 00:34:48,960
I still found the tenth son.

368
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:53,280
You had the Formless Moon
pose as the Shilin Sect

369
00:34:53,880 --> 00:34:55,679
and slaughtered the Flood Dragon clan,

370
00:34:56,199 --> 00:34:59,000
making Xie Lingxi suspicious
of the Shilin Sect,

371
00:34:59,920 --> 00:35:01,840
so he hid the son deeper.

372
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:05,960
The tenth son vanished without a trace.

373
00:35:07,360 --> 00:35:08,520
Suspicion

374
00:35:09,880 --> 00:35:12,760
is the best weapon
against the human heart.

375
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:16,400
The Shilin Sect
had no news of the tenth son,

376
00:35:17,160 --> 00:35:20,120
but I always knew where he was.

377
00:35:20,720 --> 00:35:24,000
That's because you planted
a fragment of spirit inside him.

378
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:29,920
But Wu Shiguang has grown up,

379
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:32,840
yet he hasn't become a dragon,
which made me suspicious.

380
00:35:33,360 --> 00:35:34,200
So,

381
00:35:35,080 --> 00:35:36,640
you sent the Six-Eyed Butterfly.

382
00:35:39,360 --> 00:35:40,400
Yes.

383
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,560
I had him devour a person

384
00:35:45,920 --> 00:35:47,800
to obtain his consciousness and memories.

385
00:36:05,320 --> 00:36:06,160
I knew…

386
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:10,960
you would come.

387
00:36:12,040 --> 00:36:15,800
Tell me, who exactly are you?

388
00:36:17,600 --> 00:36:18,920
I am you.

389
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:23,360
And that person

390
00:36:24,720 --> 00:36:26,600
was the former hunter commander
of the Shilin Sect,

391
00:36:26,680 --> 00:36:29,400
plagued by the Wasting Sickness

392
00:36:29,480 --> 00:36:31,440
and long missing,

393
00:36:33,280 --> 00:36:34,440
Yuan Wuhuo.

394
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:46,840
You should be familiar with him.

395
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:52,600
When I found Yuan Wuhuo,

396
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:58,080
he was a decaying man
waiting to die alone in a cave.

397
00:37:00,720 --> 00:37:04,320
Aging, gravely wounded beasts

398
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:07,800
will all, in their final moments,

399
00:37:07,880 --> 00:37:11,640
go alone into hidden forests
or deep caves.

400
00:37:13,040 --> 00:37:16,640
They don't want their own kind
to witness their death.

401
00:37:18,040 --> 00:37:21,960
That is their final pride.

402
00:39:34,840 --> 00:39:36,600
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

403
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:41,720
Who are you? Where are you from?

404
00:39:44,040 --> 00:39:45,040
I don't remember.

405
00:39:46,360 --> 00:39:47,680
What do you remember?

406
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:50,680
It seems…

407
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:53,960
I have a younger brother.

408
00:39:55,680 --> 00:39:56,520
It seems…

409
00:39:58,320 --> 00:39:59,720
I need to find him.

410
00:40:25,680 --> 00:40:29,200
To my surprise,
it took the Six-Eyed Butterfly decades

411
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:31,920
to fully consume the consciousness
and memories of Yuan Wuhuo.

412
00:40:33,040 --> 00:40:36,400
His will was unyielding,
rare in this world.

413
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:40,000
He truly was a stubborn man.

414
00:40:41,160 --> 00:40:44,080
Even the most stubborn one
can't outlast time.

415
00:40:45,360 --> 00:40:49,560
The mortal lifespan
is their greatest shackle.

416
00:40:50,720 --> 00:40:52,600
Yuan Wuhuo is no more.

417
00:40:53,720 --> 00:40:54,840
After that,

418
00:40:55,440 --> 00:40:59,760
the Six-Eyed Butterfly
roamed the world in his form.

419
00:41:01,560 --> 00:41:04,200
When the Six-Eyed Butterfly
returned to your side,

420
00:41:04,800 --> 00:41:07,000
you learned of the tenth son's secret.

421
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:09,240
It's coming soon.

422
00:41:09,760 --> 00:41:14,240
Master Chi Wen entrusted the tenth son
to a very capable person to raise.

423
00:41:14,960 --> 00:41:18,120
When he comes of age, he will come to you.

424
00:41:18,920 --> 00:41:22,360
When he comes of age,
will he become a dragon?

425
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:25,720
Like Master Chi Wen,

426
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:29,720
majestic and powerful,
soaring through the heavens?

427
00:41:30,600 --> 00:41:32,480
The tenth son is special.

428
00:41:33,120 --> 00:41:35,960
He was created from nine reverse scales.

429
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:38,160
He needs four pieces
of the Dragon Deity's Power

430
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:40,000
to awaken and become a dragon.

431
00:41:40,080 --> 00:41:41,520
First, his scales form.

432
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,640
Second, his claws grow.

433
00:41:44,480 --> 00:41:46,040
Third, his horns sprout.

434
00:41:47,600 --> 00:41:48,880
Fourth, his eyes ignite.

435
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:51,760
You were eager to obtain
the Dragon Deity's Power

436
00:41:51,840 --> 00:41:54,040
to enter Wu Shiguang's body,

437
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:56,920
so you used the fragment of spirit
planted within him.

438
00:41:57,440 --> 00:41:58,320
And subtly,

439
00:41:58,840 --> 00:42:02,240
you gave him hints,
leading him to Luo'an City.

440
00:42:03,120 --> 00:42:04,360
Every step after that,

441
00:42:05,240 --> 00:42:09,240
it's hard to say
whether it was Wu Shiguang's own will

442
00:42:10,120 --> 00:42:11,960
or your influence driving him.

443
00:42:14,240 --> 00:42:15,880
Everything you said is correct.

444
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:20,040
But for your spirit fragment
to fully control him,

445
00:42:20,960 --> 00:42:23,880
you still need to find
the dark sides in his heart.

446
00:42:25,880 --> 00:42:28,360
Wu Shiguang is not weak-willed.

447
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:31,080
After possessing him for so long,

448
00:42:31,960 --> 00:42:34,160
you've never found a way
to break his will.

449
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,280
Not before,

450
00:42:38,840 --> 00:42:39,960
but now I have.

451
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,480
You mean Wu Wangyan?

452
00:42:46,000 --> 00:42:52,440
Nothing breaks a person's spirit
more than losing what they love most.

453
00:42:53,400 --> 00:42:54,560
After all these years,

454
00:42:55,400 --> 00:42:57,960
you still don't understand
the human heart enough.

455
00:42:59,240 --> 00:43:02,520
Wu Shiguang already knows about her role
in slaughtering the Flood Dragon clan.

456
00:43:03,040 --> 00:43:04,440
His feelings for her now are complex.

457
00:43:05,400 --> 00:43:08,600
If you kill her now, it will only make him

458
00:43:08,680 --> 00:43:11,720
more determined to fight against you.

459
00:43:14,320 --> 00:43:15,920
You have a better idea?

460
00:43:17,400 --> 00:43:18,920
Let him rescue Wu Wangyan,

461
00:43:19,760 --> 00:43:22,360
let them rekindle their bond,
let their feelings grow deeper.

462
00:43:22,960 --> 00:43:24,880
Once he gathers
all the Dragon Deity's Power

463
00:43:24,960 --> 00:43:26,560
and his love for her runs deep,

464
00:43:27,320 --> 00:43:29,240
I'll kill Wu Wangyan before his eyes.

465
00:43:32,040 --> 00:43:33,720
He'll surely break down then.

466
00:43:42,720 --> 00:43:44,560
You can take the chance

467
00:43:44,640 --> 00:43:46,400
to seize his body.

468
00:43:47,320 --> 00:43:48,840
Then go to the Dragon Abyss,

469
00:43:49,360 --> 00:43:54,760
kill Chi Wen, and free your true form
from within his body.

470
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:58,120
What do you think?

471
00:43:59,920 --> 00:44:00,960
And you?

472
00:44:04,200 --> 00:44:05,280
What do you want?

473
00:44:11,840 --> 00:44:14,080
I want to remain the Dragon Deity.
